        "username": "bzzz"
      },
      "date": "2016-05-30 12:09:58.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nright, but I still think it makes sense to avoid exclusive spinlocks in read path - this will be another point of collision in FPP usecase.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
